{"tid":941042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港女兒】重播梅艷芳拉斯維加斯表演片段 梅媽稱掛住阿女","createTime":"2018-12-14T12:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T11:51:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":320,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"cc7711e37d23815994239ace9adb76a2fd613909","tid":941042,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T12:22:29.000Z","msg":"梅艷芳今年逝世15周年，梅媽覃美金特別搵番佢1999年喺拉斯維加斯舉行演唱會兩個鐘嘅片段，於12月22日喺新光戲院播映兩場。今日梅媽由阿仔梅啟明陪同喺銅鑼灣見記者，提起阿女都眼濕濕，話無時無刻都掛住梅姐。梅媽話當年自己搞緊抗癌協會冇隨團去拉斯維加斯，所以到時喺現場欣賞：「睇番啲片段佢好靚，啲人話冇人喺嗰邊整過咁靚嘅燈。我覺得應該俾人睇下，分享佢舞台精神，好多人讚賞佢係香港女兒。」<br />\n<br />\n梅媽更話當年自己並冇叫梅姐細細個就唱歌：「4個細路我都冇迫佢哋做啲乜，俾人話我4歲叫佢去唱歌，其實佢一直鍾意唱歌，學唱歌跳舞國語我都畀佢學。表弟喺荔園做，讚佢係天才，細細個唱得晒全首《賣花女》，我哋搞劇團冇迫佢唱。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8Dc1noE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8Dc1noE.png&h=56398162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n1sMyvj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn1sMyvj.png&h=334cfd57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wKZOMQk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwKZOMQk.png&h=edd5b1c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gxXArQm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgxXArQm.png&h=d00e69e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181214/59029856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F59029856&d=v1VPRN1IhJUbED0I6rncm49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=68303a20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181214%2F59029856&h=66e39cd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181214/59029856</a>"},{"pid":"229f95cea5c5367b218659eb0c4211570cd3a318","tid":941042,"uid":38904,"like":417,"dislike":1,